text: Galina Shikhova (born 11 December 1940) is a Soviet alpine skier. She competed in three events at the 1972 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1940 births Category:Living people Category:Soviet female alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of the Soviet Union Category:Alpine skiers at the 1972 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Moscow
